page.title: 07A BOY'S DAY
page.content: I rise in the Morning at 7.45 and watch T.V.a.m. until 8.15;then I wash and dress myself and have my breakfast,a plate of cereal with milk. I leave home for school at 8.45 arriving there at 9.00 School finishes at 4 p.m. and when I reach home I have my dinner and then frequently go down to the Golf Course and play a round of golf.I then phone my dad who comes down in his car and gives me a lift home. I then have my supper, play with my computer until about 10.30p.m., and then I go to bed.
